number_of_cells.description: initial number of cells (for each cell type)

number_of_fibres.description: initial number of fibres (for each fibre type)

anisotropic_fibres.description: flag for whether we want anisotropic fibres

angle_normdist_sd.description: standard deviation of fibre orientation angle

fibre_custom_degradation.description: flag for having degradation depends on pressure

fibre_stuck_time.description: time before stuck cell can degrade fibre

fibre_stuck_threshold.description: movement threshold to declare a cell stuck

fibre_pressure_threshold.description: time before stuck cell can degrade fibre

color_cells_by_pressure.description: flag for coloring cells by pressure

fibre_sticky.description: measure of how easy it is to move a fibre
